description.p:
The present invention is directed to a multilayer structure comprising at least one couple (L1-L2) of adjacent layers (L1) and (L2), wherein:
· layer (L1) comprises at least one polymer composition (C1) comprising: (i) at least one semi-aromatic polyamide, and (ii) at least one impact modifier (I1);
· layer (L2) comprises at least one polymer composition (C2) comprising: (i) at least one un-functionalized polyolefin (PO2); and (ii) at least one functionalized polyolefin (FPO2), said functionalized polyolefin comprising functional groups chosen from carboxylic groups, their esters, their anhydrides and their salts.

claim.claim-text:
A multilayer structure comprising at least one couple (L1-L2) of adjacent layers (L1) and (L2), wherein:
■ layer (L1) comprises at least one polymer composition (C1) comprising: (i) at least one semi-aromatic polyamide, and (ii) at least one impact modifier (I1);
■ layer (L2) comprises at least one polymer composition (C2) comprising: (i) at least one un-functionalized polyolefin (PO2); and (ii) at least one functionalized polyolefin (FPO2).

Structure multicouche comprenant au moins un couple (L1-L2) de couches adjacentes (L1) et (L2), dans laquelle :
• la couche (L1) comprend au moins une composition polymère (C1) comprenant : (i) au moins un polyamide semi-aromatique, et (ii) au moins un modificateur de résistance aux chocs (I1) ;
• la couche (L2) comprend au moins une composition polymère (C2) comprenant : (i) au moins une polyoléfine non fonctionnalisée (PO2) ; et (ii) au moins une polyoléfine fonctionnalisée (FPO2).
